metadata:
  version: "v1"
  identifier: "1de8f7c8-a9d8-4433-9e87-d95979ccab14"
  annotations: {}
spec:
  inputs:
    artifacts: []
    parameters:
    - name: "execution"
      type: "Map"
  arguments:
    artifacts: []
    parameters: []
  dependencies: []
  initContainers: []
  sideCarContainers: []
  pipelines:
  - apiVersion: "core/v1"
    metadata:
      provider: "pai"
      name: "id-2d88-1608982098027-91558"
      version: "v1"
      identifier: "type_transform"
      annotations: {}

Arguments.example:
---
arguments:
  parameters:
  - name: "execution_maxcompute"
    value:
      endpoint: "http://service.cn-shanghai.maxcompute.aliyun.com/api"
      odpsProject: "xxxxxxx"
